        <h2 class="title"><a href="/gallery-regular-photos-burning-man-2010">Gallery of regular photos from Burning Man 2010</a></h2>    <span class="submitted">Submitted by <a href="/user/brad" title="View user profile." rel="nofollow">brad</a> on Fri, 2011-08-12 16:40.</span>
    <span class="taxonomy"><ul class="links inline"><li class="first taxonomy_term_86"><a href="/topic/burning-man" rel="tag" title="About burning man, my other home" class="taxonomy_term_86 active">Burning Man</a></li>
<li class="last taxonomy_term_1"><a href="/archives/cat_photography.html" rel="tag" title="" class="taxonomy_term_1">Photography</a></li>
</ul></span>
    <div class="content"><p><a href=http://pic.templetons.com/brad/photo/bm10/><img src=http://pic.templetons.com/brad/photo/bm10/night/thumb/IMG_0729.JPG class=blogpic></a>As I prepare for Burning Man 2011, I realized I had not put my gallery of regular sized photos up on the web.</p>

<p>Much earlier I announced my <a href="http://pic.templetons.com/brad/pano/bman10.html">gallery of giant panoramas of 2010</a> which features my largest photos in a new pan-and-zoom fullscreen viewer, I had neglected to put up the regular sized photos.</p>

<p>So enjoy:  <a href="http://pic.templetons.com/brad/photo/bm10/">Gallery of photos of Burning Man 2010</a></p>

<p>I still need to select and caption 2007 and 2009 some day.</p>
</div>
    <div class="links">&raquo; <ul class="links inline"><li class="first blog_usernames_blog"><a href="/blog/brad" title="Read brad&#039;s latest blog entries." class="blog_usernames_blog">brad&#039;s blog</a></li>
<li class="last comment_add"><a href="/comment/reply/1126#comment-form" title="Add a new comment to this page." class="comment_add">Add new comment</a></li>
