        <h2 class="title"><a href="/three-fantastic-burning-man-stories">Three fantastic Burning Man stories</a></h2>    <span class="submitted">Submitted by <a href="/user/brad" title="View user profile." rel="nofollow">brad</a> on Wed, 2007-09-26 01:07.</span>
