        <h2 class="title"><a href="/burning-man-panoramas-2007">Burning Man Panoramas for 2007</a></h2>    <span class="submitted">Submitted by <a href="/user/brad" title="View user profile." rel="nofollow">brad</a> on Thu, 2007-09-20 15:02.</span>
    <span class="taxonomy"><ul class="links inline"><li class="first taxonomy_term_86"><a href="/topic/burning-man" rel="tag" title="About burning man, my other home" class="taxonomy_term_86 active">Burning Man</a></li>
<li class="last taxonomy_term_1"><a href="/archives/cat_photography.html" rel="tag" title="" class="taxonomy_term_1">Photography</a></li>
</ul></span>
    <div class="content"><p>I have generated several of my <a href="http://pic.templetons.com/brad/pano/bman07.html">panoramas for this year&#8217;s Burning Man</a>.</p>

<p><a href=http://pic.templetons.com/brad/pano/bman07.html><img class=blogpic src=http://pic.templetons.com/brad/pano/thumb/double-bow.jpg></a></p>

<p>This year featured a double rainbow, and of course much of the week with no man on his pedestal.</p>
</div>
    <div class="links">&raquo; <ul class="links inline"><li class="first blog_usernames_blog"><a href="/blog/brad" title="Read brad&#039;s latest blog entries." class="blog_usernames_blog">brad&#039;s blog</a></li>
