        <h2 class="title"><a href="/burning-man-2006-gallery">Burning Man 2006 Gallery</a></h2>    <span class="submitted">Submitted by <a href="/user/brad" title="View user profile." rel="nofollow">brad</a> on Thu, 2007-07-12 15:26.</span>
    <span class="taxonomy"><ul class="links inline"><li class="first taxonomy_term_86"><a href="/topic/burning-man" rel="tag" title="About burning man, my other home" class="taxonomy_term_86 active">Burning Man</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_1"><a href="/archives/cat_photography.html" rel="tag" title="" class="taxonomy_term_1">Photography</a></li>
<li class="last taxonomy_term_59"><a href="/tags/burning-man" rel="tag" title="" class="taxonomy_term_59">burning man</a></li>
</ul></span>
    <div class="content"><p>It&#8217;s way late, but I finally put captions on my gallery of regular-aspect photos from Burning Man 2006.</p>

<p><a href=http://pic.templetons.com/brad/photo/bm06><img src=http://pic.templetons.com/brad/photo/bm06/burn/thumb/IMG_8119.JPG class=blogpic></a></p>

