a boomlift.</p>

<p>I also did another aerial survey, but that remains unfinished.  Way too much processing to do, and Google did a decent one in google maps.  I did put up a few such photos there.</p>

<p>Enjoy the <a href="http://www.templetons.com/brad/photo/bm06/" title="reference on 2006 Burning Man Photos" target="_self">2006 Burning Man Photos</a>.</p>
